{"tid":2022874,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國譴責「世衛」把台灣排除WHA之外","createTime":"2020-05-18T15:04:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T03:59:52.000Z","uid":134071,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"95cd446ecfd2a17f738609636ab982c5dd4a1317","tid":2022874,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:04:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/europechinese/posts/2950152568365005\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Feuropechinese%2Fposts%2F2950152568365005&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=a9959431\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/europechinese/posts/2950152568365005</a><br />\n<br />\n歐洲動態<br />\n24分鐘 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n【臺灣世衛問題 美卿發嚴辭聲明】<br />\n世衛大會視像會議進行之際，美國國務卿蓬佩奧就臺灣參與WHA問題發表言辭異常嚴厲的聲明。<br />\n<br />\n聲明稱，美國「譴責」把臺灣排除WHA之外，指出COVID-19疫情下，多邊組織應履行使命，為全部成員的利益服務，而不是玩政治。<br />\n<br />\n聲明說，世衛總幹事譚德塞絕對有權力、亦有先例可援，把臺灣包括入WHA之內，但譚德塞礙於中華人民共和國(PRC)的壓力而不邀請臺灣，進一步損害世衛的公信力和有效性。<br />\n<br />\n聲明形容PRC把臺灣「滅聲」的舉動是「心懷惡意」(spiteful)，突顯出PRC稱希望在抗疫上具透明度和跟國際合作，只是空洞的承諾，且令中國和臺灣(China and Taiwan)之間的分別更加明顯。聲明說，臺灣是「模範世界公民」，PRC就繼續扣起病毒及其來源的重要資料，拒絕讓外國接觸中國科學家和到相關設施，對中國內及中國社交媒體上的瘟疫討論進行審查，並廣泛、魯莽地諉過於人。<br />\n<br />\n聲明又借疫情，來突顯美國推崇的自由民主價值觀。聲明說，臺灣成功抗疫，關鍵在於臺灣是具透明度、充滿生機並有創意的民主體制，這些政府永遠較專制政權更迅速和有效回應疫情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.state.gov/taiwans-exclusion-from-the-world-health-assembly/?fbclid=IwAR3ovLd7m0I551TaHGbDf7j5RkX0J8mQXdavPjIca1yVjrtngSY1boohdFg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Ftaiwans-exclusion-from-the-world-health-assembly%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3ovLd7m0I551TaHGbDf7j5RkX0J8mQXdavPjIca1yVjrtngSY1boohdFg&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=4b037459\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.state.gov/taiwans-exclusion-from-the-world-health-assembly/?fbclid=IwAR3ovLd7m0I551TaHGbDf7j5RkX0J8mQXdavPjIca1yVjrtngSY1boohdFg</a>"},{"pid":"618b42333cf473ebeba01b58e2f150937e464d83","tid":2022874,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:04:18.000Z","msg":"美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b49b3813e2a57ba47806c4c981fb95d2a664b2","tid":2022874,"uid":219269,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"618b42333cf473ebeba01b58e2f150937e464d83","tid":2022874,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:04:18.000Z","msg":"美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:05:17.000Z","msg":"歐豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79d634dfb093d9f5159395317ccca67a608b30c","tid":2022874,"uid":45914,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:06:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db43b07646ea7c64205d0d4f5f3198dd64e45172","tid":2022874,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:07:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abec22415a20cf97b8c4dfd9d37bcf079f5a6d75","tid":2022874,"uid":125193,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:07:47.000Z","msg":"我敢肯定 WHO 1,2 年898"},{"pid":"93b7c1375ba468d1b3488196ef495f2f35ad17af","tid":2022874,"uid":125193,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:08:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我敢肯定 WHO 1,2 年內bye bye </blockquote>"},{"pid":"0b92686b5abb444e73545e12e8e3a1243adb812b","tid":2022874,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:09:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/secpompeo/status/1262376762094256128\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsecpompeo%2Fstatus%2F1262376762094256128&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=331f6d92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsecpompeo%2Fstatus%2F1262376762094256128&h=fe17c208\" data-a